description:
Presented in English.
webOSroundup.com is the premier source for news, app reviews and tips for getting the most from your HP webOS devices. This app provides easy access to our articles and podcasts right from your phone. Using this app you can quickly see new and updated articles from the site formatted for easy reading on your smartphone or tablet.

Features include:
‣ View and add article comments
‣ adjustable text background & font size
‣ multiple sharing options, including saving to Relego
‣ quick links to the webOSroundup Twitter and Facebook pages

Download today and begin learning more about HP/Palm and your webOS devices.
